reviewText: Poor quality and not Jenna's best.

Jenna is amazing and this movie includes four (ONLY FOUR) scenes of hers.  They aren't bad scenes.  The problem is that the DVD was clearly made from an old VHS tape.  It starts with the usual sex line advertisements, the video quality is mediocre, and the disc itself looks homemade.  The "scene selection" breaks each scene in half, giving the illusion of eight choices, but there are really only four scenes on the disc.  Even though it's Jenna, I was disappointed.
